text: Sea Links at Birch Bay. One of the last remaining building lots within the gated community of Sea Links. Fully Serviced Lot. Water, Sewer & Power are in the Street. Ready to build. Hard to find large & very tastefully updated manufactured home in great condition with a big shop on its own land for only $349, 900! This very warm and inviting 3 bedroom home boasts a primary suite to include slate, a vessel sink, tile and wood treatments as well as 2 more bedrooms sharing an easily accessible bath w/shower & more higher end features. The open floorplan is warmed on those chilly nights by a freestanding woodstove very centrally located over an attractive tile hearth. The kitchen boasts tile countertops, pine cabinets, lots of storage in an open pantry, & nearly new appliances. Separate dining room. Partially fenced w/two sheds & a private firepit area. And the 20 x 35 foot shop is a game changer in this price range.

Discover a spectacular place for your new home! Forested, private, with Deer Creek on property, one acre - set back & distant from corner of Northwest & Axton Roads w/ private easement that leads to home - Huff Way. Mid-Century tri-level home - large front yard w/lots of parking & sunny, park-like back yard & 3-car garage almost 800 SF. Built 1958, 1, 848 SF, 3 BR & 1.75 BA w/hardwood floors. Extra living room below. Stylish interior & great space behind the home for entertaining & activities. Garden space, fruit trees & berry bushes. Mid-County w/ Bellingham address & Ferndale Schools. Close to I-5 & Bellingham shopping - COSTCO etc. A lot is going on at this home - location, forested feel in front & back, Mid-Century style + more!

Spacious lawn area w mature landscaping, a water feature, Nat Gas fire pit + large East facing deck w expansive views! Shed in backyard stays. Huge concrete stamped driveway w extra parking.

This property features a large detached garage as well as a 2200 sq. ft. shop to store just about anything you want. Currently the owners are getting paid $3, 500/year to advertise for a company on their large billboard on the property.

From the home, you'd never know you're just 10 minutes from I-5, Ferndale, Lynden, and Bellingham, and just steps from downtown Laurel. Your peaceful and move-in-ready retreat awaits you!

Help! I was a great looking home when I was built in '62 but unfortunately I was left all alone a few years back & I haven't been the same since. I'm perched on a pretty good sized lot & within walking distance to amazing Maple Beach. At my heart is a cozy fireplace to gather around & I provide 2 bedrooms & a full bathroom. I even have a new skylight that wasn't exactly planned but you can now stargaze through the roof! I'm a bit saggy on the right hand side. Looking for a long term relationship with a new owner to bring me back to my good old self or better! I'm gonna be a lot of work but hopefully a rewarding experience. Call my great broker to discuss. PS... I'm offered up at way below assessed value to make me more interesting!

Welcome to your cozy haven in the heart of convenience! Step into this meticulously maintained 2-bed, 1.75-bath home and you will be greeted by spacious vaulted ceilings and an abundance of natural light streaming though the bay windows, French doors and skylights. Ample closets, cabinet space and a handy shed outside ensure you have room for all of your treasures. Embrace peace of mind with recent upgrades including fresh interior paint & new roof, furnace & ductwork installed in 2023. Enjoy access to fantastic amenities in this 55+ community including clubhouse with kitchen for special events, pool tables, and salon by appointment. Easy access to the bus line, I5, Fred Meyer, Whole Foods, Woods Coffee & more, making errands a breeze.

Most adorable Beach Cottage ever on 50 feet of west facing waterfront! Sweeping views of Mt Baker to the east and the San Juan Islands and Salish Sea to the west. 2 bedrooms (one with Murphy Bed) and 1 fabulously updated full bath. Gorgeous finishes throughout, quartz countertops, hardwood flooring, wood built-ins galore, gas fireplace, Air Conditioning, heat pump, & mini-split. Vaulted ceiling, big wall of windows and French Doors to appreciate the sparkling blue ocean & the beach. Expansive entertainment deck and firepit on the beach. Detached garage for 1 car and plenty of additional storage space, plus off-street parking. Don't miss this opportunity to own a little piece of heaven on the beach!

Your dream home awaits! This charming rambler offers 3 bedrooms + a versatile rec room/potential 4th BR, perfect for a starter or forever home. Updated kitchen w/ new cabinets features pantry, ample counter space & a convenient dining area. Spacious primary bedroom faces the backyard & is filled w/light. Curl up by the fireplace in the living room or enjoy coffee on your back patio. Updates include NEW carpet, interior & exterior paint, roof & septic system. Nestled on a spacious 1-acre lot w/ a 24x24 barn/shop w/open stalls, garden beds & fruit trees - your hobby farm awaits. Plenty of parking & just a short jaunt from Bellingham or Lynden, this home is the perfect blend of comfort & convenience.

Located in an exceptional neighborhood near top-rated schools and beautiful Whatcom Falls Park, this charming 4-bedroom, 2.5-bath home offers convenient access to Lake Whatcom. The home features a spacious deck perfect for entertaining, overlooking a private, fenced backyard teeming with birds and wildlife. The interior is clean and move-in ready, boasting modern amenities and ample living space. The beautifully landscaped front and back yards enhance the home's curb appeal, providing a serene and inviting outdoor environment. Don't miss this opportunity to live in a vibrant community with natural beauty.

Welcome to a centrally located, charming 1940's farmhouse on a perfect piece of property! A rare find in this market! This 3 bedroom 2 bath home features all main floor living with a large living/family room and a potential bonus upstairs upon finishing the attic. Ample natural light abounds throughout a smooth floorpan making this home very inviting. Primary bedroom includes his and hers closets. Multiple well kept outbuildings including barn and a shop with a work space on almost 3 acres offer opportunity for a small homestead, hobby farm or simply a little extra space while only minutes from Bellingham, Lynden or the freeway. This perfect property won't last long!

Beautiful building lot at the dead end of quiet N Cedar Park Dr. This lightly treed lot is partially fenced, has a full culvert, storage shed and an approved 3 bedroom Glendon Biofilter septic design and permit. This is the perfect lot for your future dream home!

Serene country living in this stunning home on a picturesque 3.8-acre lot. Inside, enjoy updated floors, new doors, and a recently painted interior. Newer upgrades: roof, tankless water heater, furnace, luxurious new hot tub & setup for EV charging. Property comes prepped & permit issued for a 57x30' shop, perfect for hobbies, storage or workspace. Modern amenities w/ country charm combine to make this property a perfect home retreat!

Beyond the main residence, the property offers lots of outbuildings, including storage buildings, a nice sized shop, and a picturesque barn complete with a large hay loft. Sitting on 8 acres of prime farmland with irrigations rights, this is a truly unique opportunity to own your own piece of county paradise.

Country retreat on expansive grounds with a short trail to the Nooksack River. Just 20 minutes from Bellingham, and moments from Whatcom County's renowned eagle-watching spot. Featuring a spacious living area, the home includes two additional downstairs bedrooms and a versatile office/sunroom adjacent to the kitchen. Ample space for gardening and accommodating farm animals, with outbuildings offering limitless possibilities for vehicle storage or hobbies.

Experience the best of both worlds: enjoy the tranquility of country living on an acre while being just minutes away from local amenities. This stunning single-level home w/ a basement has it all. Don't miss this unique opportunity to own a beautifully updated home with abundant space & charming outdoor amenities.

Stunningly crafted home perfectly positioned on an expansive corner lot with custom features throughout. The main floor features extensive bamboo flooring, vaulted ceilings, a cozy gas fireplace, and a spacious patio ideal for entertaining. The primary suite on the main floor includes dual walk-in closets, a double tiled shower, and a luxurious jetted tub. Upstairs, find two additional bedrooms and a bonus room. The landscaped yard features a sports court, providing both beauty and functionality. Build your dream home on 5 serene acres with wide open gorgeous valley & mountain views w/ potential Squalicum Lake views. Recent wetlands delineation & report completed. Well installed, Power Base installed, Private Road is Paved.

Stunning, sophisticated and serene! Located in highly sought after Birch Bay Village on a very quiet street with fully fenced private backyard & expansive trex deck for entertaining. It truly does not get any better than this- no projects and plenty of time to play!

This chalet style home stands in a clearing next to a greenbelt w/views of the valley and mountainsides. The vaulted ceiling and big windows create a spacious feeling. There is a bedroom on the main floor and flex space to use as you like in the large loft. The stand up crawl space has hook ups for a washer & dryer and room for storage. It's 7 minutes to beaches @Lake Whatcom and other amenities of the Sudden Valley community. 20 min to downtown Bellingham, 55 min to BC border & 2 hrs to Seattle. Take the stairs @ #4 on Lot 31, or follow the trail through separate buildable lot 32 which adds value & options & is included in the sale. You can combine lots & lower dues, or build a house, or a garage. 15, 172 total square feet both lots.

You will love this clean, bright & open concept 3 bed, three-bath+ loft home minutes from the beach, clubhouse & boat launch! The main floor features two bedrooms; one a primary w/ full bath & a second bedroom + extra loft space (art/music studio/home office?). Brand new roof in 2021! Other updates include hand-scraped hardwood plank floors, tile, a brand-new front deck, + more. At ground level, with/ a separate exterior entrance, is a second primary bedroom w/ a 3/4 bath. An excellent short-term rental opportunity or overflow for your guests! A private backyard features terraced decks, gorgeous cedar, & fir trees, making it an oasis of calm. Go crabbing and exploring for the day from the boat launch & come home to this beautiful spot.

Nice homes in this waterfront neighborhood.

This home is truly a Puget Hill gem!

Experience PNW year round, at this beautiful at Snowater Resort. Endless amenities to create lifelong memories. Endless trails throughout the complex, Nooksack river, Mt. Baker National Forest, you've got access to every outdoor activity you can imagine! This condo is turn-key with everything you could possibly need included! Snowater Resort has popular amenities, such as two indoor pools/hot tubs, a sauna, indoor sports courts, tennis, two playgrounds, a gym, lounge areas, picnic areas, outdoor BBQs, & so much more. Large open living area with 10' ceilings on the main floor, fireplace and vinyl plank flooring, open living, dinning and kitchen area gives you the feeling of a much larger space. A short drive to town, I-5 or the Canadian Border. 20 minutes commute to Bellingham.

Located on a quiet & private cul-de-sac, surrounded by mature cedars & perfectly situated on a beautifully landscaped 1/3-acre lot, this 4 bedroom residence is sure to please! The upper level consists of 4 generous bedrooms + a den each w/ adequate space that offers comfort & convenience. Other features include: the large 3-car garage, new roof/gutters (2022), & fresh paint throughout. All within walking distance to the golf club & other amenities.

Amazing estate property with so much potential to create your dream home, with gated access to the neighborhood, future Canadian Rocky views and the ultimate in privacy. There's a forestry plan in place that will allow several acres to be cleared to capitalize on the views and create a nice open building site with lots of natural light. You don't want to miss out on this amazing 20 acre lot!

Sitting at the end of Jimi Hendrix Way, this lot offers ultimate privacy where you will be surrounded by a canopy of trees and abundant nature. Outside Bellingham city limits gives many options for how to use this property. This is the opportunity you've been waiting for!

This ONE-LEVEL living beautiful craftsman 3bd 2ba home in a small community of 10 homes & a park is now available.You will fall in love entering the home with gorgeous interior designs featuring hardwood floors, thoughtful open kitchen/living space W/ granite counters, custom backsplash, stainless appliances and perfect kitchen island facing the amazing fireplace wall with custom mantle, shelving and tv/electronics area &wired for inwall speakers.Warm interior colors, custom ceiling fans, lighting, fixtures & high ceilings that make this home feel larger than the sq footage would lead.Screened-in/ covered back porch for entertaining looks out over the professionally landscaped grounds with green belt behind. Oversized two-car garage W /workspace

Another great new home in Hannah Creek by Skeers Construction. Phase 5 is already more than half sold out! Gorgeous setting backs to a forested greenbelt with creek. Modern, great room floor plan features main floor primary and home office / flex room. Bonus room and two bedrooms on upper floor. Miles of trails to explore on the adjacent 3000 acre Galbraith Mountain trail system, and Whatcom Falls Park is just down the street. Feels like a world apart, but downtown is less than 3 miles away. Scheduled for end of August completion.

Exquisite home in the Evergreen Neighborhood in Ferndale. Boasting 1774 square ft, on a large corner lot, with 4 bedrooms and 2 baths on the upper level, and all the living on the main. Separate living and family rooms, dining room, dining nook, and kitchen with eating bar. This place has got space for everything! Private, shaded space in the backyard, perfect for the weekend get togethers to cook some s'mores over the built-in fire-pit!

Situated in the sought after Columbia neighborhood, this single-level duplex is perched on West St with easy access to Squalicum Parkway. Embark on a leisurely walk to Squalicum Creek Park complete with a playground, off-leash dog park, sledding hills in the west corner of the park. Each unit has two beds and one bath and W&D. Recent updates in unit 102 include new kitchen, bathroom, flooring, lighting. Sitting on a larger lot, there is potential for expansion. Find your way home in the well established Columbia neighborhood known for its walkability to downtown, parks, breweries and its peaceful, picturesque character year round.

One-owner home waits for new steward on the trails of south Alabama Hill. Faithfully maintained for 50+ years by the descendants of Bellingham founders, this 1-level home has had the hard work done-- you just get to choose colors. Newer roof, ext paint, furnace & H2o, kitchen appliances, windows & ext doors, plumbing fixtures, gas fireplace and electrical. Eat-in kitchen opens to the living room & to the den w/ sliders to the large, flat, sunny yard. Primary bedroom has walk-thru closet and continental access to the full bath. Lots of storage throughout including in the 2-car attached garage. Zero-traffic location at the intersection of two non-thru streets just steps from 240-acre Whatcom Falls Park. Trails literally in every direction.

Rare find! 2 remarkable homes 1 block away from Lake Whatcom! Live in one & rent the fully furnished ADU to subsidize your mortgage. Main home is custom-built to perfection & situated for maximum southern exposure. Bespoke cherry cabinets provide plenty of storage in thoughtfully designed kitchen. Dining/living room is perfect for parties. Primary suite fts huge walk-in & en-suite w/artisan tile-work, walk-in shower & dual vanities. Upstairs rec room framed for 3rd bedroom/office. Fenced yard w/raised garden beds, fruit trees & deck w/awning, perfect for enjoying summer nights. Grab a paddleboard & stroll to the neighborhood beach, walk to school, visit Stimpson Reserve or hop on a bike & shred Galbraith. SO much more, don't miss out!

The Ivy by MainVue Homes at Horizon is a stunning design you do not want to miss. Upon entry find a soaring Two-Story Foyer a corner set a Home Office. Deeper into the home, the Two-Story Great Room is paired perfectly with a sophisticated Dining room and mutually connected Gourmet Kitchen flush with 3cm Quartz counters, Stainless Steel Appliances, and a Grand Butlers Pantry. For even more space, a main floor Multi-Purpose Room is tucked just off the kitchen. Upstairs, look out onto the Great Room from the front-facing Leisure room that leads to three secondary bedrooms and the luxurious Grand Suite. Customer registration policy: Buyers Broker to visit or be registered on Buyers 1st visit for full Commission is reduced.

Nearly new, beautifully built & in excellent condition for your immediate move-in! This easy-to-own 4-yr-old home features an Open Layout w/spacious kitchen flowing to a dining area then family room w/a cozy gaslog fireplace! Primary BR on the main floor includes walk-in + en suite bath. Upstairs are 3 large guest BR's & full bath. The walk-out basement features a Rec Room for the main living area in one half, then an income-generating, legal, attached ADU that is vacant now but was just rented at $1600/mo. ADU has a full kitchen, laundry hook-ups, studio sleeping area & 3/4 bath. Separate entrance & parking make this set-up practical & profitable! B'ham's owner-occ. requirement ends with HB1337 & both units become rentable like a duplex.

Charming NO STEPS 3 bedroom rambler is freshly updated & ready for you to call it home! Recent upgrades include on-trend light grey cabinetry, massive kitchen island, stainless steel appliances + white doors & trim. Flexible floor plan with open concept kitchen/living/dining space also opens to bonus room w/ wood burning fireplace. It's nearly impossible to find a stick built home in this price range w/ the freedom of a no HOA neighborhood. Fully fenced private backyard with covered area is the ideal place to relax or entertain. 2 car attached garage, storage shed & RV parking...all just minutes to booming downtown Blaine. It's an easy stroll to the schools, shopping, dining, parks & marina or a quick drive to the US/CAN border & I-5.

Beautiful new construction quality built by Pacific Edge Builders custom home on quiet dead end street. Desirable Whispering Meadows neighborhood is Nooksack's newest development surrounded by protected open space and waterways. This one level 3 bed, 2 bath home features open concept living space which truly feels large. Primary bedroom with walk in closet, tiled flooring and backsplash w/ quartz countertops. Kitchen with stainless appliances, quarts countertops, full height backsplash tile & custom cabinets w/ addl pantry space in dining. Located close to schools, parks, restaurants, & the Canadian border. Hydroseed and landscaping in planter beds to be installed prior to closing and included in the purchase price. Vacant & move in ready!

Custom home is on 2.51 acres of nature completed in Q4 2022. No steps throughout the home for true single level living. Custom features are extensive and numerous: 8' tall solid fir doors, 8' tall custom cherry/art glass front door, solid natural cherry kitchen cabinets in the large gourmet kitchen, oversized walk in pantry, stone core 100% waterproof luxury laminate floors. Open concept living, dining and kitchen. 7.1 surround sound wired living room, 120 motorized ALR projection screen that disappears when not in use. Hide-away lighted display area for valuable collections (whiskey not included). Workshop space in heated garage. 30x60x16 shop built in 2023. Enjoy the hummingbirds from the patio. Full 50A RV hookup No HOA, and more!

This private property is perfectly situated to take in views of the surrounding mountains and amazing sunrises! Two parcels totaling 20 ac and abutting DNR land, an additional home could be built on the property. The freshly painted home has a professionally designed chef's kitchen, and has an abundance of cherry shaker cabinets with quartz countertops, a 5 burner gas Wolf cooktop and double wall ovens, as well as separate refrigerator and freezer (in the walk-in pantry). The living areas are all open and look to the mountains with vaulted ceilings and floor to ceiling windows. There's a 16'x32' in-ground pool, woodshed, 3 car garage, greenhouse, art studio and much more! Build another house and/or ADUs and enjoy the serenity and views.

Ground is broken on this stunning new home from Slusher Luxury Homes. This home will have it all. Long list of upgrades! 4 bdrm, 3.5 bath home with 4 car tandem garage & coveted Southside schools. Large kitchen with Soft-close cabinet doors & drawers, Thermadore commercial appliances, quartz countertops with a 9' eating bar & spacious walk-in pantry & extra wide h/w floors. Open floor concept on the main floor complete with 8' tall interior doors, a 46 linear gas f/p and grand study. Great dining area that will easily seat 8. Spacious primary bdrm suite complete with a w/ 6' luxurious shower & dual sinks. Plus 1 of 2 large covered decks. Modern design, extra high ceilings, expensive TPO roof. Ductless mini split & central a/c too!

Brand new townhome in Bellingham's Sunset Village community. This 3 story, 3 bedroom, 1.75 bath end unit features an oversized garage, stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops & mixed cabinetry. Walkable to shopping, dining, bus line, & trail system. Don't miss out on a great opportunity!

This ground-floor condo in the heart of Bellingham is a rare find at this price, offering a great opportunity for investors and first-time home buyers. The high ceilings enhance the spacious and inviting feel of this one-bedroom unit. Enjoy the private, covered back patio, which extends your living space. With secure parking, a courtyard, and elevator access, this condo ensures convenience and peace of mind. Your neighbors include Whole Foods Market, Civic Stadium, Bellingham Bells Ball Park, Arne Hanna Aquatic Center, Fred Meyer and Whatcom Falls Park. In Western Washington University bus line to boot. No rental cap!

Fantastic southside location, walking distance from the historic Fairhaven area with eateries, groceries and every amenity one could need. This ground floor, one level 2 bed 1.75 bath light and bright condominium is not only an amazing location but is also a turnkey 55+ residence ready for the next owner. At 1224 square feet, plus a detached garage with storage, zero steps, new paint and freshened carpets in great shape, there is nothing to do but move right in and enjoy the proximity to all Fairhaven has to offer. Just steps from the interurban trail, this home allows for easy access to activities and good lifestyle choices, all on a manicured site! Enjoy large bedrooms, a spacious and well lit kitchen, plus 2 private patios too!

Attention 1st-time home buyers and investors! Discover this classic single-story Blaine home in a quiet cul-de-sac, surrounded by larger residential neighborhoods. Just minutes from downtown Blaine amenities, Canadian border, schools, and I-5, this 1, 484 sqft contemporary home features 3 bedrooms, 1.75 baths, and an unfinished sunroom (approx. 100 sq ft) that opens to a patio. The primary suite includes a bathroom with a walk-in shower. Enjoy two separate family/living rooms, one with a custom fireplace centerpiece. Large, fully-fenced backyard w/a patio is perfect for entertaining guests. New H2O tank in 2020, Furnace in 2021 & roof in 2022. Don't miss out on this opportunity to buy a single-family home w/no HOA at a great price!

First time on the market for this custom designed 2015 Marlette home, located in the highly desirable Portal Creek Park, an age 55+ community. The exceptional floorplan features 2 bedrooms, 2 baths, an office, a laundry room with extra storage/sink and an oversized 2 car garage with plenty of room for your RV or boat! A beautiful, fully fenced backyard adjacent to a wooded area, provides one of the most private lots in the community and plenty of shady comfort from your back patio. The only owners have meticulously maintained the home and has desirably features such as extra insulation in the walls, insulated plumbing and a highly efficient heat pump A/C system. Come see worry free living at its finest!

This immaculately maintained 3-bed, 2-bath home in Lynden offers the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and security. With 1, 900 s.f. of living space, this home features a whole-house Natural Gas generator, a sprinkler system, security system, central A/C, high-end window coverings, updated flooring, updated appliances and much more. The large 11, 575 s.f. corner lot provides ample space for outdoor activities, while the fully fenced, manicured backyard offers a private oasis for outdoor living plus a custom-built workshop, gazebo, and hot tub covered by a pergola. Conveniently located across from the new Lynden Middle School, this home is an exceptional choice for folks seeking a peaceful, secure, and well-appointed living environment.

The wait is over! A rare opportunity to own a lot in beautiful Sandy Point on the canal. Build your dream home on this level and easy to build lot located in a quiet cul-de-sac with views of Lummi Bay, Georgia Strait and Mt. Baker. With 80 feet frontage on the canal with dock and gangway. Power on property with a 50 amp on lot, and 30 amp at the dock for boat plug. Take advantage of all that the Sandy Point community has to offer with so many great amenities including golf, swimming pool, clubhouse, tennis & pickleball, marina, and more!
nearby_schools: Lummi Elementary School, Ferndale School District, Lummi High School

text: Water and North Cascade Mountain View, Main floor living area bathed in sunlight, Built in 2017, 4 bedroom, 3.75 baths, plus private office, 3300 sq. ft. 3-level home with elevator, granite counters, engineered hardwood floors, elegant finishes, lots of closets, main floor living room, 2nd level family room, Central air conditioning, three decks give home lots of outdoor living space to enjoy the view and sunny days. Two seperate entrances. Unbelievable heated 6-8 car garage for all the toys(1700Sq.Ft.), with 1/2 bath, located 1/2 mile from salt water marina, lots of parking. Sandy Point Community Membership available if you choose. Amenities include, marina, golf course, clubhouse, swimming pool, sports courts & organized activities.
nearby_schools: Lummi Elementary School, Ferndale School District, Lummi High School

text: This stunning custom home has it all! Grand 2-story entry w/office, open floor plan with spacious living rm and gas fireplace, dining room & kitchen with granite counters, ss appls & walk-in pantry. Main floor features beautiful hardwood floors throughout! Patio doors open to large deck for entertaining and just steps away to the Hot tub and fenced backyard. Huge primary bedroom with double door entry, fully tiled walk-in shower, jetted tub, double vanity & walk-in closet. 2 more bedrooms + bonus room upstairs. Daylight basement is perfect for entertaining w/ a Theater room, wet bar, rec room, sauna and 4th Bd w/ensuite bath. 2-car garage +workshop area, shed in backyard and in-ground sprinkler system. Call today for your private viewing!
